    question: '<p>What will be rendered within the <code>div</code> with <code>id="main"</code>?</p>\n<pre><code class="language-jsx">function Exercise(props) {\n    return (\n    &#x3C;div id="main">\n        {props.children}\n    &#x3C;/div>\n    );\n}\n\nReactDOM.render(\n  &#x3C;Exercise>&#x3C;h1>Main&#x3C;/h1>&#x3C;/Exercise>,\n  document.getElementById(\'root\')\n);\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>???</code></p>\n',
